overview: Angela White and AGW Entertainment bring you the fifth installment of the multi-award winning series, Angela Loves Women. Angela White directs and stars in every scene alongside top performers Autumn Falls, Ana Foxxx, Alina Lopez and Natalie Mars. Angela Loves Women 5 presents these all-natural women in tender encounters that showcase genuine passion, chemistry and lust. This is sex as it should be: raw, intimate and real.
title: Angela Loves Women 5
